<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>6266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>9496</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家好！我是一封信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9497</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>11883</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哎！我很累。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11884</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>15879</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>因为我刚刚完成一趟长途旅行。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>15880</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>18371</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的旅行有多远？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>18372</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>让我告诉你！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25708</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两天前，一个小女孩儿给她的奶奶写了一封信。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25709</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>30207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把信叠好，放在我身体里面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>30208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“舔一舔我的信封口，然后抚平！”我告诉她。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35910</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40009</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把奶奶的地址写在我的身上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她在我的身上贴了一张邮票。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44266</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>46579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我看起来不精致吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>46580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49429</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她把我放进邮箱里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49430</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>52998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邮箱里真的很黑！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>52999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>在邮箱里，我遇到了其他的信封。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62354</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>有的比我小，有的比我大。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62355</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>每一封信都要去某个遥远的地方！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70207</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>突然，邮箱的门被打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70208</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73776</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们都被放进一个大口袋里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73777</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后我们乘车出发了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>77874</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>哇！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>77875</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81575</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我从袋子里偷偷向外望去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81576</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>84002</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们要坐飞机了！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>84003</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>88107</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当我们落地时，袋子被打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>88108</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90218</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我们到了邮局。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90219</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>96075</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个机器正快速地把我们分类到不同的盒子里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>96076</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>100795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后一个女邮递员把我拿了起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>100796</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103578</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再见！再见！”我说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108410</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女邮递员带着我走到了一条街上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108411</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113035</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喂！这是谁的家？”我问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113036</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116274</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，我到了奶奶的家！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116275</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>119513</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>到了她把我打开的时间了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>119514</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>122623</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哎呦，小心点！”我说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>122624</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125685</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>奶奶见到我非常开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125686</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>127714</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我也很开心。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>127715</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>133024</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在我有了一个温暖的新家！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
